  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Sites</h1>

  <h2 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">Our allotment sites and rent charges</h2>

  <div class="prose-page mt-4">
    <p>
      The Allotments Association runs five sites on behalf of the City of Ely Council. We do not
      administer the site at Deacons Lane, Ely nor do we have a firm date when the new allotment
      sites to be constructed in the North Ely housing development will be opened. The existing
      sites where plots become available are shown below. Click on the images for details.
      <a href="#rents">Details of rent charges</a> for allotment plots are on this page below the
      site summaries. The <a href="/info/#tenancyagreement">Tenancy Agreement</a> defines the
      terms of rental and occupation of an allotment plot.
    </p>
  </div>

